df_high <- df %>% 
  mutate_at("value", str_replace, pattern = "\\*", replacement = "5") %>% 
  mutate_at("value", as.numeric) %>% 
  group_by(district, type) %>% 
  mutate(fouryr_val_high = sum(value)) %>% 
  ungroup() %>% 
  filter(year == 2017) %>% 
  select(ring, district, type, fouryr_val_high)
